00:06:09.443 --> 00:06:11.117
Play, they were all about play

143
00:06:11.117 --> 00:06:13.304
in their films and in their interviews.

144
00:06:13.304 --> 00:06:15.362
Huge influence on me.

145
00:06:16.452 --> 00:06:21.138
So I was shy as a musician when I was quite young.

