176
00:07:24.576 --> 00:07:27.456
You know my older brother, we were I'd have to say

177
00:07:27.456 --> 00:07:30.400
competitive sibling rivalry, all this kind of stuff.

178
00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:34.511
