00:12:05.374 --> 00:12:06.622
has a clue as to who they are.

287
00:12:06.622 --> 00:12:09.022
I think it's charming and adorable that people

288
00:12:09.022 --> 00:12:10.920
think that they know who they are.

289
00:12:10.920 --> 00:12:11.834
(laughter)

290
00:12:11.834 --> 00:12:14.843
I think that's great, but to me, and I'm not judging

291
00:12:14.843 --> 00:12:16.070
anyone's self-concept.

292
00:12:16.070 --> 00:12:18.353
It's just, the ones that work for me are the ones

