00:14:02.235 --> 00:14:03.696
"the time, you just don't realize that.

336
00:14:03.696 --> 00:14:05.082
"I mean look at you, you don't look like

337
00:14:05.082 --> 00:14:07.077
"anybody else, you don't dress exactly like

