00:15:26.746 --> 00:15:28.417
is a whole creation itself.

368
00:15:29.817 --> 00:15:31.769
But the point being, is that the more we open up

369
00:15:31.769 --> 00:15:36.388
to what creativity is, the more we just allow it.

370
00:15:38.328 --> 00:15:39.289
Can I keep rambling here?--

371
00:15:39.289 --> 00:15:40.516
<v Voiceover>Please do, please do--</v>

