00:16:08.481 --> 00:16:10.667
judgement involved from day one.

385
00:16:10.667 --> 00:16:12.427
Is it gonna to be good?

386
00:16:12.427 --> 00:16:14.379
And there to me is the biggest obstacle

387
00:16:14.379 --> 00:16:18.379
for inspiration and creativity is, is it good?

388
00:16:18.379 --> 00:16:19.723
But what does good mean?

389
00:16:19.723 --> 00:16:20.672
And here we go--

390
00:16:20.672 --> 00:16:22.077
<v Voiceover>So highly subjective.</v>

